cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL

The paper proposes a machine learning framework for Alzheimer's disease classification using multiple kernel learning. This falls under the broad category of machine learning (cs.LG) and specifically involves computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. The use of group lasso regularization also suggests a potential connection to neural networks (cs.NE) and natural language processing (cs.CL) applications.
